lead_paragraph: Sindarius Thornwell had 19 points and eight rebounds and No. 22 South Carolina remained undefeated with a 69-65 victory over Vanderbilt on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 South Carolina Remains Unbeaten With Win Over Vandy
